descriptionHtml:
my first mod

a dark elf follower in riften bee an barb. he will have dialogue unique to him soon. He will have a back story revolving about the balmora thieves guild. He will have a quest soon with new npcs. He will also have a home just outside riften. The bee and barb is only temporary. He was kicked out of morrowind because he still worshipped the false tribunal ( ALSIVI ). He is wanted by house redoran and telvani. He was a member of house hilalu.

No bugs

Please endorse

Enjoy
author: Vivec123456789
